{"tid":2125834,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"星座撚之金牛座乜都有tg谷","createTime":"2020-07-26T12:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T00:51:40.000Z","uid":217514,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a266c72fb635947f89573e8e5d58ae724493948","tid":2125834,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:44:38.000Z","msg":"《性格保守且沈穩的金牛座男生，如同歸隱詩人般追求安穩恬靜的田園生活。》<br />\n《八面玲瓏的金牛座女生，恰到好處的交際手腕總能贏得眾人的好感。》<br />\n<br />\n金牛座不嬲都唔係好多人理解到㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身為金牛座嘅你嚟圍爐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然大家都未必係星座撚 但主要想搵返同星座嘅人嚟吹水<br />\n仲可以搞下生日聚添<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然都歡迎想溝金牛座仔仔/女女嘅你嚟問下各位大師如何入手<br />\n<br />\n依個谷乜都吹得 唔歡迎藍絲呀！明㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n活動都會搞 想乜聚有乜聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對狗公娘娘表示強烈不了 你做咩都會有人知㗎<br />\n當然你要扮你喺金牛都唔緊要 只係無乜意思～<br />\n其他星座jj有意入嚟分享你嘅故事求救好歡迎㗎！<br />\n<br />\n間唔時會清人 有意入嚟就填form<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/S5mp1GyocoSDZdNk7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FS5mp1GyocoSDZdNk7&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=828bdc3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/S5mp1GyocoSDZdNk7</a>"},{"pid":"fc796491c598d87f6514e1f85c0257eb0deb2b73","tid":2125834,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLY8VVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLY8VVs.png&h=a38ce796&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ed8b929153acaef1b31122e5ee98f6163ab4d68","tid":2125834,"uid":191937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:12:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"942ffca564d35ff0a2134ec638adcc624a4240d0","tid":2125834,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl